description: Whether its soccer season or not the Mini Team Soccer Shoe Key Chain can surely add some element of style and country team pride. Quality made in fine details almost as real as the actual soccer shoe features your team national flag emblem and country name in bright colors representing your favorite soccer team. Using only the finest materials ensuring you best quality that will endure the test of time. Excellent as company giveaways or to add to your personal soccer collectibles these soccer shoes keychains express your team loyalty and love of the game.
